  <p><strong>Note</strong>: Donâ€™t use more than 6-7 characters for <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;$SERVICE_NAME&gt;</code>. 8 character words might take several days to generate, even on a modern CPU. If you have some GPU power, you can use <a href="https://github.com/lachesis/scallion"><em>Scallion</em></a> to speed things up.</p>
</blockquote>

<ol>
  <li>Install <em>OpenSSL</em> libraries and some build tools:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>apt update
apt <span class="nb">install</span> <span class="nt">-y</span> libssl-dev build-essential
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Download <em>Eschalot</em>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wget https://github.com/ReclaimYourPrivacy/eschalot/archive/master.zip
unzip master.zip
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Build <em>Eschalot</em>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">cd </span>eschalot-master
make
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run <em>Eschalot</em>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>./eschalot <span class="nt">-vct</span><span class="si">$(</span><span class="nb">nproc</span><span class="si">)</span> <span class="nt">-r</span> <span class="s2">"^&lt;</span><span class="nv">$SERVICE_NAME</span><span class="s2">&gt;"</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

